                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "defensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> The glass golem is targeted by a spell</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The glass golem positions its magical, reflective surfaces to turn the spell back on the caster. It tries to counteract the spell by attempting an Acrobatics check for its counteract check. If it successfully counteract the spell, the effect is turned back on the caster.</p>"
